  },
  "transcript": [
    {
      "turn": 1,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Priyansh, cricket finals are always exciting — what snack are you choosing for the MI vs CSK match?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I think I'll go with some pav bhaji and cold drinks. It's a classic combo for me. How about you?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Nice choice — pav bhaji and cold drinks are perfect for a cricket match. I’m curious, which player are you rooting for in the final?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I'm supporting MI, obviously! I'm a big fan of Surya Kumar Yadav. What about you?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Got it — MI has a strong team this season. Surya Kumar Yadav is a smart pick. Are you watching the final with friends or alone?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "With friends, definitely! We usually gather at a small watch party. Sometimes even watch in the office if the game is on a weekday. You?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Great — office watch parties are fun too. Will you take your pav bhaji to the office or eat it at home first?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "At home first. We usually start the match with a pre-game feast, then head to the office for the actual match. It's more comfortable. 😊"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Sounds like a perfect plan — feast first, then the action. Will you and your team stream the match or watch it on TV?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "We usually stream it on our phones or a laptop — it’s easier if we’re all in a small room. Sometimes we even use a projector if the office space allows. You know, keep it casual but game-ready! 😄"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Love the casual setup — phones, laptops, even a projector if space allows. What’s your go-to drink while streaming the match?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Soft drinks, mostly. Sometimes we get some beer if it's a weekend gathering. But mostly just chilled soda — easy, refreshing, and no mess! 😊"
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Chilled soda is a solid choice — no mess, easy, and refreshing. Are you planning to root for MI with some team chants or just watch quietly?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "We usually cheer a lot, especially when MI scores. Team chants, clapping, and sometimes even some fake commentary — it gets pretty fun! Quiet is for when CSK are batting, obviously 😂"
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Fake commentary and team chants sound like a winning setup — especially when MI scores! What’s your favourite moment from this season so far?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 9,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "My favorite moment was when MI chased down that 200+ total in the semi-final. Surya was on fire that day — what a knock! Just pure thrill, you know? 😄"
    },
    {
      "turn": 9,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Chasing 200+ is always thrilling — Surya’s knock was amazing. Will you and your team take a break during the final or watch it all at once?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 10,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "We’ll probably watch it all at once — no breaks, no distractions. We want to feel every twist and turn, you know? Like a movie marathon but with cricket! 😄"
    },
    {
      "turn": 10,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Movie marathon energy for the final — no breaks, no distractions. Got it. What will you do if MI wins? Any traditions?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 11,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "If MI wins, we’ll definitely celebrate — maybe grab some dinner or order pizzas! Sometimes we even head to a local pub if it's a weekend. But if CSK win... well, we’ll pretend we didn’t care, right? 😂"
    },
    {
      "turn": 11,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Pretending not to care if CSK win is the best strategy — classic! What’s your all-time favourite MI victory?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 12,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hmm, tough one! But I think the 2019 final against CSK was the best — what a game! Surya and Quinton de Kock really carried the team. That moment when they won... unforgettable. 😊"
    },
    {
      "turn": 12,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"2019 final vs CSK — what a game! Surya and Quinton’s chase was magic. Will you relive that moment during the final or focus only on the present?\""
    }
  ],
